{"tid":919750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳凱欣「突破界限」？　帶家人入立法會影相被請離場","createTime":"2018-11-28T09:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T05:43:17.000Z","uid":1886,"like":111,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"cb2d4ae8b94d2a5bb6405fd160c119333bc31abe","tid":919750,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:36:49.000Z","msg":"剛履新的立法會議員陳凱欣今日宣誓，父母同丈夫邱文華都特意嚟見證佢呢個重要時刻，其間發生一段小插曲。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181128/s00001/76f6ab439d1df8ce1c606926aa7ea52b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181128%2Fs00001%2F76f6ab439d1df8ce1c606926aa7ea52b.jpg&h=9d2ce841&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n話說一見到陳凱欣家人，攝影記者當然不斷影相。但係根據指引，議員訪客並唔能夠喺立法會大樓內受訪，所以立法會職員都馬上請阿欣家人離開，最終佢哋只能夠喺大樓入口外面影相。其間阿欣影相時有兩聲咳，爸爸都輕拍佢膊頭，場面溫馨。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181128/s00001/771142b8b87cac9be42f1fb53de1f708.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181128%2Fs00001%2F771142b8b87cac9be42f1fb53de1f708.jpg&h=7f071fb8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n根據立法會《採訪指引》第24段，傳媒只能夠喺立法會外面訪問公眾人士，阿欣被請離場之後就話，因為想遵守規則，希望大家可以將立法會大樓內影嘅相「抹咗佢」。<br />\n<br />\n到底阿欣今次係咪「突破界限」呢？阿欣助手解釋話，因為阿欣啱啱履新嘅關係，立法會未畀指引佢哋；Emily聽攝記同事講，助手一早同佢哋講阿欣會帶家人落嚟，所以佢哋先擺好陣預備，仲話係阿欣拉媽咪過嚟影相。<br />\n<br />\n睇番《立法會綜合大樓議員辦事處使用指引》，喺立法會或其轄下委員會舉行會議期間，議員訪客除了到訪2樓觀景廊或2樓或3樓公眾席外，不可進入會議場地所在的樓層(即立法會綜合大樓1樓或2樓)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181128/s00001/1543381517141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181128%2Fs00001%2F1543381517141&d=%2BWpD9ZlUq4iJirSvHYEh%2BG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c556ed3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181128%2Fs00001%2F1543381517141&h=f8a03d5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181128/s00001/1543381517141</a>"},{"pid":"140aa40ad0d18f4aa85f621013db81112d08727d","tid":919750,"uid":23829,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:38:14.000Z","msg":"4突陳凱欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98f43edf7da098082b396790c2946706d7349f2","tid":919750,"uid":36901,"like":205,"dislike":0,"score":205,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"真係狗改不了吃屎<br />\n咁撚鍾意搞特權"},{"pid":"cf5489c49a40abac1c805d08b4f79829d367098d","tid":919750,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c35391d1504a4ca84dc7bed7677078a570eee1","tid":919750,"uid":208799,"like":1,"dislike":43,"score":-42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:45:05.000Z","msg":"記者影相關被影果個咩事?"},{"pid":"f7bb995134fe017b27b39e4ca6162941a39ca589","tid":919750,"uid":17646,"like":177,"dislike":0,"score":177,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:47:56.000Z","msg":"自己做開政助成日出入立法會同我講唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dabf1c3568935a8724c5d3f565aca7d4986e361","tid":919750,"uid":200328,"like":211,"dislike":0,"score":211,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:48:56.000Z","msg":"建制派有特權<br />\n犯事都唔洗DQ<br />\n本土派犯啲仲未立既法就即刻DQ<br />\n<br />\n公平咩"},{"pid":"079648db424d5375db98d4bf456be3e2a1c46ca2","tid":919750,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"110lv"},{"pid":"8e95744ed88b2e4502e476bece9361e457b0d569","tid":919750,"uid":106426,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"126eaf11f72ae06f94335515d81f89d96eeb4557","tid":919750,"uid":54516,"like":1,